item.title: About Me 👩‍💻
item.description: Hello, my name is Noha and I am a software engineer and data scientist with expertise in machine learning. I began my career as a software engineer, where I honed my skills in algorithm development and programming. After two years in the industry, I took a break to explore other interests and gain new experiences. During this time, I discovered a passion for data science and machine learning. I decided to pursue this interest by diving into various online courses and attending workshops.
